  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Strategy and Partner Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Partner Alliance Executive</strong></p><p><strong>Core Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Relationship Management:</strong> Manage and enhance strategic relationships with existing partners\nwhile onboarding new ones to drive revenue.</li><li><strong>Growth Facilitation:</strong> Coordinate engagement between partners, sales, and pre-sales teams to accelerate business growth.</li><li><strong>Ecosystem Networking:</strong> Collaborate with startups, founders, and vendors to align on technology roadmaps and understand the market landscape.</li><li><strong>Strategic Insights:</strong> Translate market trends and internal capabilities into actionable insights and innovative solutions.</li><li><strong>Data-Driven Reporting:</strong> Analyze large datasets to identify trends and create dashboards or presentations for management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>IT Industry Expertise:</strong> Strong background in the IT industry with a broad knowledge of technology and a passion for new trends.</li><li><strong>Corporate Diplomacy:</strong> Excellent interpersonal skills and the ability to maintain professional diplomacy in partner management.</li><li><strong>Analytical Skills:</strong> An analytical mindset capable of processing complex data into meaningful reports.</li><li><strong>Team Collaboration: </strong>A strong team player who can manage diverse stakeholders effectively</li></ul><p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)</p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>Gwen@talentsis.com.sg </strong>or connect in Whatsapp <strong>+65 6421 4960 </strong>for immediate processing.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
